Package edu.citadel.cprl.ast

Interface NamedDecl

All Known Implementing Classes:
ParameterDecl, SingleVarDecl
public interface NamedDecl
Interface for a named declaration, which can be either a "single" variable declaration or a parameter declaration.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    int getRelAddr()
    Returns the relative address (offset) of the variable declared with this named declaration.
    ScopeLevel getScopeLevel()
    Returns the scope level for this declaration.
    int getSize()
    Returns the size (number of bytes) of the variable declared with this named declaration.
    Type getType()
    Returns the type of this named declaration.
    void setRelAddr​(int relAddr)
    Sets the relative address (offset) of the variable declared with this named declaration.
